src:
Disse cruiseskipene kommer til Trondheim i 2020
07 Nov 2019, 06:02 by Martin Andersen
Trondheim havn venter rekordmange cruiseanløp i Trondheim.
Det ventes hele 100 cruiseanløp i Trondheim i 2020, det viser en foreløpig oversikt fra Trondheim havn.
text:
These cruise ships will arrive in Trondheim in 2020
07 Nov 2019, 06:02 by Martin Andersen
Trondheim port awaits record cruise calls in Trondheim.
As many as 100 cruise calls are expected in Trondheim in 2020, a preliminary overview from Trondheim port shows.
